<LegalLayout title="Delete Your Account" appName="That's So Random!" lastUpdated="June 17, 2026">

  <p>
    If you would like to delete your <strong>That's So Random!</strong> account and have your personal
    data removed from our systems, follow the steps below. This page is provided by
    <strong>Refuge &amp; Sword Publishing LLC</strong> in accordance with Google Play and Apple App Store
    data deletion requirements.
  </p>

  <h2>How to Request Account Deletion</h2>
  <p>To delete your account, send an email to:</p>
  <p>
    <a href="mailto:support@refugeandsword.com" style="color: var(--heritage-gold); font-size: 1.05rem;">
      support@refugeandsword.com
    </a>
  </p>
  <p>Use the subject line: <strong>Account Deletion Request — That's So Random!</strong></p>
  <p>Include the following in your message:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>The email address associated with your That's So Random! account.</li>
    <li>A brief statement that you would like your account and data deleted.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We will process your request and confirm deletion within <strong>30 days</strong>.</p>

  <h2>What Gets Deleted</h2>
  <p>Upon confirmed deletion, the following data will be permanently removed from our systems:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Your email address and account credentials.</li>
    <li>Your premium purchase record and associated purchase tokens.</li>
    <li>Any account-linked preferences or settings.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>What Is Retained</h2>
  <p>
    We do not retain personal data after account deletion except where required by law.
    Anonymized or aggregated data that cannot identify you may be retained for operational purposes.
  </p>
  <p>
    If your purchase was processed through the Apple App Store or Google Play, those platforms
    maintain their own transaction records independently of us and subject to their own privacy policies.
  </p>

  <h2>Questions</h2>
  <p>
    If you have any questions about this process, contact us at
    <a href="mailto:support@refugeandsword.com" style="color: var(--heritage-gold);">
      support@refugeandsword.com
    </a>.
  </p>

</LegalLayout>
